'''洞角'''（{{lang-en|horn}}）是[[牛科|牛科]]动物（[[牛|牛]]、[[羊|羊]]、[[羚|羚]]等）頭上堅硬的突起物（[[犄角|犄角]]）。

==特点==
洞角一般不分叉<ref name=":0">{{Cite web|title=Horns and Antlers|url=https://animaldiversity.org/collections/mammal_anatomy/horns_and_antlers/|accessdate=2020-10-20|author=Bies, LeeAnn; Myers, Phil|date=|format=|work=The Animal Diversity Web|publisher=University of Michigan|language=|archive-date=2021-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210414085615/http://animaldiversity.org/collections/mammal_anatomy/horns_and_antlers/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，由两部分组成：[[骨骼|骨]]质的芯和[[角蛋白|角]]质的鞘；骨质芯表面有一层[[皮肤|皮肤]]。<ref>{{Cite web|title=「角」色不同|url=https://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/NewsLetter/92/185/7-1.pdf|accessdate=2020-10-20|author=張鈞翔|date=|format=PDF|publisher=國立自然科學博物館|language=|archive-date=2020-10-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201023094255/https://web2.nmns.edu.tw/PubLib/NewsLetter/92/185/7-1.pdf|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":1">{{Cite book|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YJ4rDgAAQBAJ&pg=PA31|publisher=Princeton University Press|date=2017-03-14|isbn=978-1-4008-8744-6|language=en|first=Peter|last=Dodson|title=The Horned Dinosaurs: A Natural History|year=|location=Princeton, NJ, US|pages=31|access-date=2020-10-20|archive-date=2020-11-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201123044227/https://books.google.com/books?id=YJ4rDgAAQBAJ&pg=PA31|dead-url=no}}</ref>通常两性都长洞角。<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":2">{{Cite web|title=Horns versus Antlers|url=https://www.nps.gov/articles/yell-horns-vs-antlers.htm|accessdate=2020-10-20|author=Yellowstone National Park|date=2017-08-02|format=|work=U.S. National Park Service|publisher=U.S. Department of the Interior|language=en|archive-date=2021-02-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210208005258/https://www.nps.gov/articles/yell-horns-vs-antlers.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=":3">{{Cite web|title=Horns and Antlers: What's the Difference?|url=https://www.amnh.org/explore/news-blogs/news-posts/horns-and-antlers-what-s-the-difference|accessdate=2020-10-20|author=|date=2016-08-31|format=|publisher=American Museum of Natural History|language=|archive-date=2021-02-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210227124229/http://www.amnh.org/explore/news-blogs/news-posts/horns-and-antlers-what-s-the-difference|dead-url=no}}</ref>某些[[蜥蜴|蜥蜴]]（如[[角蜥|角蜥]]<ref>{{Cite journal|title=Notice of the orbicular lizards, or horned agamas|author=Harlan, R.|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=NUYV0uBQz7MC&pg=PA384|journal=The American Journal of Science and Arts|issue=2|doi=|others=|year=1837|volume=31|page=383-385|pmid=|access-date=2020-10-20|archive-date=2020-10-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201022170501/https://books.google.com/books?id=NUYV0uBQz7MC&pg=PA384|dead-url=no}}</ref>）和[[恐龙|恐龙]]（如[[角龙亚目|角龙亚目]]<ref name=":1" /><ref>{{Cite web|title=The Horned Dinosaurs|url=https://www.amnh.org/exhibitions/dinosaurs-ancient-fossils/display-or-defense/the-horned-dinosaurs|accessdate=2020-10-20|author=|date=|format=|publisher=American Museum of Natural History|language=|archive-date=2021-01-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210126173542/https://www.amnh.org/exhibitions/dinosaurs-ancient-fossils/display-or-defense/the-horned-dinosaurs|dead-url=no}}</ref>）亦具有洞角。

洞角一般是永久性的，不会脱落。[[叉角羚|叉角羚]]角虽然结构与牛科动物的洞角类似，但是有分叉，而且角质鞘会每年脱落更新，因此有时算作洞角<ref name=":2" />，有时算作一种介于洞角和[[鹿角|鹿角]]之间的特殊类别的角<ref name=":0" /><ref name=":3" />。

==作用==
洞角可以作為武器，用來攻擊、防衛、威嚇，也能建立在族群中的地位，可以與同類雄性競爭以爭奪雌性。

==用途==
洞角可以用于制作[[乐器|乐器]]、[[容器|容器]]、装饰品，水牛角可以做成[[印鑑|印鑑]]。

==虛構的洞角==
一些虛構生物或神鬼也长有洞角，如中国神话中的[[獬豸|獬豸]]，[[西遊記|西遊記]]中的[[西遊記角色列表|金角大王和銀角大王]]，西方神话中的[[潘_(希腊神话)|潘]]、[[独角兽|独角兽]]、[[魔鬼|魔鬼]]，日本神话中的[[鬼_(日本)|鬼]]等等。

==其他类型的角==
[[鹿角|鹿角]]没有角质层，只有骨质实角。新角表面有一层皮肤，长成后皮肤脱落。骨质实角也会每年脱落更新。

[[长颈鹿科|长颈鹿科]]的角由骨质角和外部包圍的皮膚组成，称为[[皮骨角|皮骨角]]。

[[犀角|犀角]]是完全由角质纤维凝合而成，没有骨质芯，终生也不会脱换，称为表皮角。

鳥類中的[[馬來犀鳥|馬來犀鳥]]頭上有一個銅盔狀、類似角的突起，叫做盔突。

[[甲蟲|甲蟲]]中的[[獨角仙|獨角仙]]、[[兩棲類|兩棲類]]中的[[蛙|蛙]]、魚類中的[[箱魨科|箱魨科]]也有类似“角”的构造。[[一角鲸|一角鲸]]的角則是變異的[[牙齿|牙齿]]。

